Hello Alessandro,

There are several possible circumstances that can cause heritrix to visit
the same url more than once, but nothing you&#39;re likely to see often with
configuration similar to the default. Check crawl.log. Could be something
to do with the way your custom module is written or configured that
produces the behavior you&#39;re seeing.

